✅ Java 8 (March 2014) – Major Upgrade
	Lambda Expressions
	Functional Interfaces
	Streams API
	Default and Static Methods in Interfaces
	Optional<T> Class
	Method References
	Date and Time API (java.time)
	Nashorn JavaScript Engine
	Collectors and Functional-style operations
	Repeatable Annotations
	Parallel Array Operations (Arrays.parallelSort)
✅ Java 9 (September 2017)
	Module System (Project Jigsaw)
	JShell (REPL)
	Private Methods in Interfaces
	Stream API Enhancements (e.g., takeWhile, dropWhile)
	Factory Methods for Collections (List.of(), Set.of(), etc.)
	Improved Process API
	Multi-Release JARs
✅ Java 10 (March 2018)
	Local Variable Type Inference (var)
	Application Class-Data Sharing (AppCDS)
	Garbage Collector Improvements
	Root Certificates
✅ Java 11 (September 2018) – LTS Release
	New String Methods (lines(), strip(), isBlank(), etc.)
	Local var in Lambda Parameters
	HttpClient (standardized from incubator)
	Running Java files without compiling (java Hello.java)
	Removed Java EE and CORBA modules
✅ Java 12 (March 2019)
	Switch Expressions (Preview)
	Compact Number Formatting
	JVM Constants API
	Shenandoah GC (experimental)
✅ Java 13 (September 2019)
	Text Blocks (Preview) — multi-line strings with """
	Dynamic CDS Archives
	Reimplement Legacy Socket API
✅ Java 14 (March 2020)
	Switch Expressions (Standardized)
	Records (Preview)
	Pattern Matching for instanceof (Preview)
	Helpful NullPointerExceptions
	NVM support with Foreign-Memory Access API (Incubator)
✅ Java 15 (September 2020)
	Text Blocks (Standardized)
	Sealed Classes (Preview)
	Hidden Classes
	Edwards-Curve Digital Signature Algorithm (EdDSA)
	ZGC and Shenandoah improvements
✅ Java 16 (March 2021)
	Records (Standardized)
	Pattern Matching for instanceof (Standardized)
	JEP 338: Vector API (Incubator)
	Unix-Domain Socket Channels
	Strong Encapsulation of JDK Internals
✅ Java 17 (September 2021) – LTS Release
	Sealed Classes (Standardized)
	Pattern Matching for switch (Preview)
	Enhanced Pseudo-Random Number Generators
	New macOS Rendering Pipeline (Metal)
	Deprecation of RMI Activation
✅ Java 18 (March 2022)
	UTF-8 by Default
	Simple Web Server API
	Vector API (Third Incubator)
	Code Snippets in JavaDoc
✅ Java 19 (September 2022)
	Virtual Threads (Preview) – Project Loom
	Structured Concurrency (Incubator)
	Pattern Matching for Switch (Second Preview)
	Record Patterns (Preview)
	Foreign Function & Memory API (Preview)
✅ Java 20 (March 2023)
	Scoped Values (Incubator)
	Virtual Threads (Second Preview)
	Record Patterns (Second Preview)
	Pattern Matching for Switch (Third Preview)
	Foreign Function & Memory API (Second Preview)
✅ Java 21 (September 2023) – LTS Release
	Virtual Threads (Stable)
	Structured Concurrency (Preview)
	Record Patterns (Stable)
	Pattern Matching for Switch (Stable)
	Sequenced Collections
	String Templates (Preview)
	Unnamed Classes and Instance main() methods (Preview)
	Foreign Function & Memory API (Stable)
